description: Dr. Martens 1460 Boot Jean-Michel Basquiat gives you the opportunity to rock the legendary style of one of the most iconic figures in art history today. Forged with a unique collaboration between Dr. Martens and Jean-Michel Basquiat, this special edition boot offers more than just style—it’s a statement. It features high quality Smooth leather quarters that are emblazoned with one of his most celebrated pieces, ‘Untitled,’ (1982) as well as a detachable backstrap containing Basquiat’s powerful crown motif for added flair. No detail is spared with this classic boot—from its signature black and yellow scripted heel loop and sole pad print to a standout lace jewel accessory on the tongue, this boot has it all. Completely handcrafted and presented in bespoke packaging to elevate the occasion, you won’t want to miss out on owning a piece of art history with Dr. Marten’s 1460 Boot Jean-Michel Basquiat!
